Subject: Imagine.fp
Date: Thu, 09 Jun 94 09:28:00 PDT
From: Richard Morris <RichardM@agby1.agric.wa.gov.au>

>Does anyone know where I can get hold of a copy of Imagine2.0.fp, as I've 
just
>ordered a 68882 FPU?

> BYE BYE from Martin at Aber!

